{"tid":435843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加泰一係獨立不成，一係就打仗打個國家出黎","createTime":"2017-10-14T15:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T12:34:27.000Z","uid":108894,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"bea644f371291d13f0ac83a09571649f1d4f7d1f","tid":435843,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T15:48:44.000Z","msg":"世界上可以和平獨立嘅國家係少之又少<br />\n好多殖民地都係自己組軍打贏宗生國獨立<br />\n中共都要打贏民國先可以統治大陸<br />\n總結：加泰隆尼亞一係就被西班牙收回主權成為一個國家，一係真係好有心獨立的話，請自行組織軍隊同西班牙戰鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：真心覺得加泰同西班牙最終會打仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88ff8bc6217a26eed5b1b89617c56a7e7e64745","tid":435843,"uid":427,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T15:51:56.000Z","msg":"已發展國家點會打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n非洲咩"},{"pid":"7792a9e4cc0b935b89c26ea935ee4a0b2c377c8f","tid":435843,"uid":108894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:04:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已發展國家點會打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n非洲咩</blockquote><br />\n唔搞打嘅話咪等住西班牙收番加泰自己統治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果加泰真係好有民族意識嘅，一定會準備好同西班牙作戰，唔關發展唔發展事"},{"pid":"52ba09ca8d8165833dbfd60b9c8da51743393fd5","tid":435843,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:38:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>已發展國家點會打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n非洲咩</blockquote><br />\n唔搞打嘅話咪等住西班牙收番加泰自己統治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果加泰真係好有民族意識嘅，一定會準備好同西班牙作戰，唔關發展唔發展事</blockquote><br />\n好難講 到底係民族意識定係經濟驅使<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e639a1f5b22125a8cca487f9dc142e0